* Woods, Rex. &quot;One man&#x27;s desert: the story of Captain Pip Gardner, VC, MC&quot; Kimber, 1986 
* obituary in &quot;The Times&quot; (London)
*&quot;The Register of the Victoria Cross&quot; (This England, 1997)

